action_item.content:
Extract all action items and tasks from the following email.

Return a JSON array of tasks with this exact format:
[
  {
    "task": "Clear description of the task",
    "deadline": "Specific deadline if mentioned, otherwise 'Not specified'"
  }
]

If no tasks are found, return an empty array [].

Email:
From: {sender}
Subject: {subject}
{body}

Respond with ONLY valid JSON. No markdown, no explanation, just the JSON array.
